00:25:49,290 --> 00:25:50,550
Ochutnaj to.

345
00:25:50,730 --> 00:25:53,460
Uvaril som to úplne sám.

346
00:25:53,470 --> 00:25:55,950
Je to dobré a taktiež veľmi zdravé.

347
00:26:17,780 --> 00:26:19,250
Aké to je?

348
00:26:19,250 --> 00:26:21,850
Ujove cestoviny sú výborné, však?

349
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:25,590
Nechcem, aby to bol môj ujo.
Nemôže byť mojím ockom?

350
00:26:28,740 --> 00:26:32,070
Bolo by super,
keby ste boli mojimi rodičmi.

351
00:26:36,500 --> 00:26:37,770
Chceš to ochutnať?

352
00:26:38,180 --> 00:26:39,440
Čo je to?

353
00:26:39,450 --> 00:26:41,620
- Hruška.
- Dobre.

354
00:26:43,540 --> 00:26:45,480
- Aká je?
- Výborná!

355
00:26:52,820 --> 00:26:53,840
Daj si ešte.

356
00:26:58,560 --> 00:27:01,060
- Poď sem.
