Idem za vami.

384
00:29:33,660 --> 00:29:34,740
Odíď!

385
00:29:35,050 --> 00:29:36,920
Jednoducho odíť!

386
00:29:37,230 --> 00:29:39,150
Nič to nie je.
Som v poriadku.

387
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:41,160
Odíď.
Odíď...

388
00:29:41,550 --> 00:29:43,230
Nie, neodchádzaj!

389
00:29:44,320 --> 00:29:45,390
Zostaň tu.

390
00:29:46,670 --> 00:29:47,720
Ji Hyeon.

391
00:29:49,260 --> 00:29:50,330
Neodchádzaj.

392
00:29:52,530 --> 00:29:53,600
Ste v poriadku?

