408
00:31:50,090 --> 00:31:51,150
Povedzte mi prečo...

409
00:31:53,500 --> 00:31:55,710
Povedali ste,
že je Soo Ho veľmi chorý.

410
00:31:57,100 --> 00:31:58,800
Má to s tým niečo spoločné?

411
00:32:01,140 --> 00:32:02,600
Odpovedzte mi.

412
00:32:03,270 --> 00:32:05,140
Akou chorobou trpí?

413
00:32:06,180 --> 00:32:07,710
Ak vám všetko poviem,

414
00:32:09,850 --> 00:32:12,370
skutočne pre jeho dobro odídete?

415
00:32:13,720 --> 00:32:14,910
Sľubujem.

416
00:32:15,820 --> 00:32:16,870
Na oplátku

417
00:32:18,390 --> 00:32:20,250
mi povedzte pravdu o všetkom.

418
00:32:21,930 --> 00:32:23,310
Potom zmiznem na niekoľko mesiacov,

419
00:32:24,060 --> 00:32:25,660
nie-len na jeden.

420
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:28,020
Dobre.

421
00:32:29,600 --> 00:32:31,230
Čoskoro by ste sa to aj tak dozvedeli.

422
00:32:33,440 --> 00:32:34,870
Soo Ho...

423
00:32:42,910 --> 00:32:43,950
Hej.

424
00:32:43,950 --> 00:32:45,170
Pôjdem do Ameriky.

