452
00:34:19,780 --> 00:34:20,930
Hlúposť.

453
00:34:23,710 --> 00:34:25,250
Čomu mám veriť?

454
00:34:29,120 --> 00:34:31,560
Vás nezožiera svedomie?

455
00:34:34,430 --> 00:34:37,650
Nemali by ste trpieť viac ako Soo Ho?

456
00:34:39,630 --> 00:34:41,640
Preto sa to teraz snažím napraviť.

457
00:34:42,870 --> 00:34:45,180
Urobím všetko, čo mi poviete.

458
00:34:46,300 --> 00:34:48,410
Ak mi neveríte,
spýtajte sa ho na to sama.

459
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:51,470
Alebo klamete

460
00:34:52,610 --> 00:34:53,960
a netúžite po novom živote...

461
00:35:02,050 --> 00:35:03,950
<i>Anjel z dvoma tvárami?</i>

462
00:35:11,430 --> 00:35:12,550
Áno, pane.

